\textbf{OSTI:} \texttt{1484740}\quad\textbf{Authors:} Bayerl, Islam, Jones, Protasenko, Jena, Kioupakis (2017)\quad\textbf{Domain:} Condensed Matter / 2D Materials DFT-GW-BSE\\
